oc-number\">9</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Expert Advice</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">10</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Full Directory</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">11</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Owner &amp; Franchise</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">12</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">FAQs</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">More Resources</span></button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-actions\"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn toc-action-top\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-up\"></i>Back to Top</button><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-down\"></i>To Bottom</button></div></div></div><main class=\"city-page-layout\"><div class=\"mobile-toc-button\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"mobile-toc-trigger\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-ul\"></i><span>Contents</span></button></div><section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Cleveland</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">Better City Barks</p><h1>Dog Parks in Cleveland, TN</h1><p class=\"hero-description\">Cleveland is committed to pet-friendly living, featuring facilities like the Dog Park at Jack Benson Heritage Park and proximity to Benton Falls Trail.</p><div class=\"city-rich-description\"><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Cleveland, TN, is a shining example of pet-friendly community planning, actively participating in the &quot;Better Cities for Pets&quot; program. The city features the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.clevelandtn.gov/Facilities\">Dog Park at Jack Benson Heritage Park</a>, offering two separate fenced areas for large and small dogs, complete with water stations, agility equipment, and double-gated entry. Nature enthusiasts can explore <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://tnstateparks.com/parks/red-clay\">Red Clay State Historic Park</a>, where 263 acres of trails, ridges, and the Blue Hole Spring provide scenic leashed adventures. Nearby, the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/cherokee\">Benton Falls Trail</a> within Cherokee National Forest offers a 3-mile dog-friendly path to impressive waterfalls.</p><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Cleveland&#x27;s downtown district has embraced pet-friendly policies, with over 40 businesses displaying signage to welcome pets, including banks, boutiques, and restaurants with patios like <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://champyschicken.com/\">Champy&#x27;s Famous Fried Chicken</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.mashandhops.com/\">Mash &amp; Hops Craft Beers</a>. Pet owners must adhere to strict leash laws and licensing requirements, ensuring a safe community for all. While Cleveland&#x27;s outdoor options are abundant, seasonal weather variations can impact plans. <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\">Indoor Dog Park</a> provides year-round reliability, offering a climate-controlled sanctuary where Cleveland&#x27;s dogs can maintain their exercise and socialization routines regardless of outdoor conditions.</p></div><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->15+ verified spots</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Cherokee Forest access</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Cleveland dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/cleveland-tn/hero.webp\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Cleveland</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Cleveland<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Verified ratings, review volume, and park availability updated directly from our community directory.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Community rating</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">4.8</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Average rating across every verified listing in Cleveland. Reflects cleanliness, amenities, and community feedback.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Verified reviews</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">7,966</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Community reviews informing our quality score. Tap any park card below to see highlights.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Park availability</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">41</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Total verified listings currently live for Cleveland. Fresh listings added weekly.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Indoor options</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">—</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Indoor options are being scouted—submit a favorite and we will feature it.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-header\"><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">Most common amenities</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">What people are looking for and finding in <!-- -->Cleveland<!-- -->.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Onsite services</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Indoor facilities</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Professional staff</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">10