:\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Cleveland is committed to pet-friendly living, featuring facilities like the Dog Park at Jack Benson Heritage Park and proximity to Benton Falls Trail.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Cleveland, TN, is a shining example of pet-friendly community planning, actively participating in the \\\"Better Cities for Pets\\\" program. The city features the \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.clevelandtn.gov/Facilities\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Dog Park at Jack Benson Heritage Park\"}],null,\", offering two separate fenced areas for large and small dogs, complete with water stations, agility equipment, and double-gated entry. Nature enthusiasts can explore \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://tnstateparks.com/parks/red-clay\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Red Clay State Historic Park\"}],null,\", where 263 acres of trails, ridges, and the Blue Hole Spring provide scenic leashed adventures. Nearby, the \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"7\",{\"href\":\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/cherokee\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Benton Falls Trail\"}],null,\" within Cherokee National Forest offers a 3-mile dog-friendly path to impressive waterfalls.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Cleveland's downtown district has embraced pet-friendly policies, with over 40 businesses displaying signage to welcome pets, including banks, boutiques, and restaurants with patios like \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://champyschicken.com/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Champy's Famous Fried Chicken\"}],null,\" and \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.mashandhops.com/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Mash & Hops Craft Beers\"}],null,\". Pet owners must adhere to strict leash laws and licensing requirements, ensuring a safe community for all. While Cleveland's outdoor options are abundant, seasonal weather variations can impact plans. \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"7\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Indoor Dog Park\"}],null,\" provides year-round reliability, offering a climate-controlled sanctuary where Cleveland's dogs can maintain their exercise and socialization routines regardless of outdoor conditions.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],\"$L12\"]}],\"$L13\"]}]}],\"$L14\",\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\",\"$undefined\",\"$L1a\",\"$L1b\",\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\",\"$L1e\"]}]\n9:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-new\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"IndoorDogPark\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\